{{Otheruses|Shrike}}
'''''Shrike''''' was an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] which served in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The frigate was [[Attack on the Shrike|attacked]] and destroyed by three [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wing starfighters]], one of them piloted by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]], and four [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptors]]. After the ''Shrike''{{'s}} destruction, a pair of [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]], designated [[Banshee (corvette group)|''Banshee'']], and a number of [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wings]] arrived at the same location, only to be destroyed by the same strike force.

